We can even know what a friend who leave thousands of miles away eat for lunch on though these kinds of social media .
From some point of view , really has a lot of advantages by let us to communicate with friends cheaper and more conveniently .
However , its disadvantages can also be ingnored when you cosider it as a platform to show off and a stage for cyber crime .
